&lt;p&gt;Syner-G was recently honored with BioSpace&#39;s prestigious &quot;Best Places to Work&quot; 2026 award, for the third consecutive year, along with many other award-winning programs to make a career here truly life-enhancing. These recognitions are a testament to our commitment to fostering a positive and engaging work environment for our employees, with a particular emphasis on culture, career growth and development opportunities, financial rewards, leadership and innovation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
